extends base

block content
  main.main
    section
      h1 Privacy Policy
      p
        | At DNS Lookup Tool, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting any personal data you share with us. 
        | This Privacy Policy outlines the types of information we collect, how we use it, and your rights regarding your data.

    section
      h2 Information We Collect
      ul
        li Basic contact details, such as your name and email address, if provided.
        li Technical information, including your IP address, browser type, and operating system.
        li Usage data related to how you interact with the site.

    section
      h2 How We Use Your Information
      ul
        li To provide and maintain the functionality of the DNS Lookup Tool.
        li To respond to your inquiries or feedback.
        li To monitor and improve our services.

    section
      h2 Third-Party Sharing
      p
        | We do not sell, trade, or share your personal data with third parties except as necessary to comply with legal obligations 
        | or to protect the rights, property, and safety of our users and others.

    section
      h2 Data Security
      p
        | We use industry-standard practices to protect your data from unauthorized access, disclosure, or misuse. 
        | However, no system can be completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute data security.

    section
      h2 Your Rights
      ul
        li You have the right to access, update, or delete any personal data we hold about you.
        li You can contact us to exercise these rights at any time.

    section
      h2 Contact Us
      p
        | If you have questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please 
        a(href='/contact') contact us.
